  m_text: 'Blast through bug swarms, dodge the chaos, and scrape together enough
    cash to survive one more sector.

    Upgrade your ship between waves, grab risky
    power-ups, and turn the screen into a very loud light show.

    Every few levels,
    something much bigger decides you have been doing too well.'
